{{Quote|The writer in me says [Cordé] served her literary function and there really is no need for her to continue after that. However, the actress in me says 'Hold on. Had Cordé not done her duty, there would be no Padmé, no flirting with Anakin, no Luke, and no Darth Vader! There would be no saga!'|Verónica Segura|<ref name="SWI136">{{InsiderCite|136|In Their Own Words: The Cast on the Making of Episode II}}</ref>}}
'''Verónica Segura''' is a [[Wikipedia:Mexican people|Mexican]] actress who played the [[Handmaiden/Legends|handmaiden]] [[Cordé/Legends|Cordé]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].

Besides ''Attack of the Clones'', she has appeared in such films as ''Tribe'', [[Wikipedia:Subterano|''Subterano'']], ''Dame tu Cuerpo'', [[Wikipedia:Club Dread|''Club Dread'']], and ''A Proposito de Alexa''.

